description:
Today on BEYOND the DARKNESS The Bermuda Triangle Incident & Powers of Intention with John Tenney.

Resaercher, author and public speaker John Tenney has spent the better part of his life exploring the strange & claims to the supernatural. Today he visits with us to discuss a few very powerful experiments he led that will send chills down your spine and we take on a challenge that we will implement on an upcoming event.

Visit John's site here: http://weirdlectures.com/
